node.text: Jets advance to 2-0 in the preseason with a 23-14 win over Green Bay! Another week of joint practice with the Eagles up next followed by their final preseason game on Friday, then it’s onto the real thing 💪 #NYJvsGB #Jets #Packers

node.text: It's GAMEDAY! After a couple of joint practices, the Jets are at Lambeau Field this afternoon to take on the Packers in their second preseason game. Zach Wilson and the rest of the starters are expected to get a little more playing time than they did last week. Kickoff is at 4:25 PM ET and will be shown on NFL Network. #NYJvsGB #Jets #Packers
